('95148','32819','5','Spacious villa in country style for sale with 6 bedrooms near Can Picafort for sale'),
('95149','32820','5','The villa is located in the east of Mallorca. The beaches of Can Picafort is only a few minutes away. On a plot of 151.000m² this chic villa was built in country style 2006. The main house has 2 living floors, with 400sqm of living space, a large entrance hall, living room with fireplace, dining room, kitchen with pantry, 3 bedrooms with a bathroom en suite. The guest house is about 100 meters away from the main house and has 420m² of living space on 3 bedrooms each with en suite bathroom, a living room with fireplace, dining room and kitchen. Another building up to 500m² of living space could be built. For high-quality facilities include, air condition w/c, double glazed windows and floorheating /cooling system (over heat pump, solar colectors and geothermal collectors). The Mediterranean landscaped garden with palm trees, almond, olive, orange and fig trees can be irrigated with water from their own wells. A 60m² large pool and many terraces invite you to relax.'),
